posts.subject: Gunwriters current and past
posts.body: A good place for these materials

>>3300c61a-af35-4942-bd16-54176887b066
Gunwriter 2015-2020

Parent company of USAToday took over smaller paper then deleted 8 years of work.

His new clearnet home: https://thegunwriter.substack.com/p/the-gun-writer-is-back

This is the same host that Tabbi and Greenwald use. It's where all the incorrigibles now go to hang their heads in shame :)

Having trouble here. Millchan is choking on zips. So I was forced to post raw.
